  "title": "Chewbacca Confronts Piper",
  "summary": "An agitated Chewbacca tracks down the CSA official Piper in Memorial Park on Etti IV, where she sits throwing a stick for her dog Duke. He confronts her over the cub Kuxli being shot, demanding to know why she has turned to coercion. Piper coolly explains that she assigned protective ESPO guards to the cub for the Authority's interests, and that his attempt to flee provoked the harsh measures taken. Chewbacca, disgusted, accuses her of sounding like the Empire and warns that such intrusiveness bodes ill for any alliance before lumbering out of the park, leaving Piper to resume her game with the dog, her expression carefully blank.",
